column.name: Query
column.value: "insert into RM_PRICE_CLOUD(PRODUCTNO,TABLENO,PRICEDATE,PRICEENDDATE,PRICE,[FILENAME],DAYNO,SENDTOCLOUD,ID) SELECT PRODUCTNO,TABLENO,PRICEDATE,PRICEENDDATE,PRICE,[FILENAME],DAYNO,SENDTOCLOUD,ID FROM RM_PRICE_STAGE where SENDTOCLOUD = 'I'"

column.name: Query
column.value: "update rm_price_cloud set RM_PRICE_CLOUD.PRICEDATE = RM_PRICE_STAGE.PRICEDATE, RM_PRICE_CLOUD.PRICEENDDATE = RM_PRICE_STAGE.PRICEENDDATE, RM_PRICE_CLOUD.PRICE = RM_PRICE_STAGE.PRICE, RM_PRICE_CLOUD.FILENAME = RM_PRICE_STAGE.FILENAME from RM_PRICE_STAGE where RM_PRICE_CLOUD.ID = RM_PRICE_STAGE.ID"
